subTitle: The struggle against a dangerous gambling lord tests Dharam Singh and Vijay as they navigate crime, deception and violence to protect the innocent and reclaim what was lost.

title: Kundan
subTitle: Thakur Shamsher Singh, a wealthy criminal, tries to befriend a newly-appointed police officer in order to gain his favour, only to find out that the policeman is immune to his tactics.

title: Satya
subTitle: Satya gets acquainted with Bhiku Mhatre, an underworld boss, while serving a term in jail and joins his gang. When he falls in love with Vidya, he is forced to choose between his job and his love.

title: 15th August
subTitle: Nagpal kills Chaudhry and his son, Ram, a military officer. Chaudhry's second son, Vikram, vows to destroy Nagpal who is all set to become the Chief Minister on the upcoming Indian Independence Day.

title: Majaal
subTitle: Vijay Kumar, an orphan, is brought up by an advocate. While he falls in love with his daughter and marries her, he struggles to cope with the humiliation he faces from her family.

subTitle: Vikram and Raju are brothers who work in a restaurant. When a conniving person frames Vikram in a murder case and separates them, circumstances lead Raju to a life of crime.

title: Naseeb
subTitle: The lives of friends Namdev, Raghu, Damu and Jaggi take a turn for the worse when they win a lottery. Raghu and Damu murder Jaggi and frame Namdev who later returns to seek revenge.

title: Baazigar
subTitle: A cold-blooded killer with a vendetta charms a businessman's elder daughter and then kills her in a way that would make it seem like a case of suicide. He then plots to destroy the rest of the family.

title: Devta
subTitle: An ordinary taxi driver becomes part of a notorious gang through a twist of fate and takes on the role of a terrifying assassin.

title: Guddu Ki Gun
subTitle: A womanising salesman gets cursed by one of his lover's grandfather for jilting her. However, the only solution to break free of the curse is for him to find true love.

title: Khel
subTitle: Three fraudsters trick a rich elderly woman, Sulakshana, who is desperately looking for her long-lost grandchild, in order to acquire her estate and property.

title: Sikandar Sadak Ka
subTitle: When Sikander, a union worker, tries to stop his employer's misdeeds, the authorities jail him. After his release, Sikander is determined to seek revenge.

title: Sultanat
subTitle: Sultan, a brave warrior, tries to win the affections of Yasmin, a beautiful woman. However, his life turns upside down when his father is killed by a general, whom he swears revenge against.

title: Khiladi
subTitle: A group of four friends decide to play a prank involving the fake kidnapping of one of them and asking for ransom from her father. However, things become complicated when she actually ends up dead.

title: Bulandi
subTitle: Dharamraj Thakur, the head of a village, is highly respected by the villagers, However, his dignity is at stake when his younger brother, Arjun, is accused of raping a school teacher.

title: Gangaajal
subTitle: IPS Amit Kumar, an honest police officer, is tasked with curbing Tezpur's rampant crime rates. Here he must work with his fellow corrupt officers and deal with the town's insidious political figures.

title: Daraar
subTitle: Raj Malhotra, a wealthy man, falls for Priya. However, things get complicated when Vikram, Priya's abusive husband, enters the frame.

title: Kaun Kare Kurbanie
subTitle: Arjun Singh, a police inspector, lives peacefully with his family in Mumbai, until an alarming case of harassment and murder turns his life upside down.

title: Anokhi Ada
subTitle: Lalaji and Gupta, two business partners, take their relationship to the next level when their children, Rakesh and Neeta, marry each other. However, chaos ensues when Lalaji helps Gopal, a stranger.

title: Ram Balram
subTitle: Unaware of his evil intentions and his role in killing their parents, two brothers Ram and Balram fall victim to their deceitful uncle. They must unite to foil his plans of gaining wealth.

title: Aakhri Ghulam
subTitle: Bheema and his family live under the tyranny of their master, Daulat Singh. But, when Bheema revolts, his love for his master's daughter is threatened.

title: Phool Aur Kaante
subTitle: Love leads Ajay down a new path when he is expected to inherit his father's criminal empire, bringing along perils that could either tear their family apart or solidify their bond.

title: Kranti
subTitle: Sanga, a devout employee of Raja Laxman Singh, is falsely accused of killing him. He escapes prison and forms a group of revolutionaries with the sole aim of driving the British out of India.

title: Dhadkan
subTitle: Anjali and Dev's love story faces a harsh twist when Anjali is forced to marry Ram. Years later, Dev returns to rekindle their romance, only to find that Anjali has grown to love her husband.
